thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-light.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Laura Mercier Caviar Smoothing Matte Refillable Lipstick\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch. A look at the latest reformulations for lipstick, liner and cream eyeshadow from Laura Mercier.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2024/10/new-laura-mercier-caviar-collection-launch.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-deep.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Laura Mercier Caviar Smoothing Matte Refillable Lipstick swatches\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch. A look at the latest reformulations for lipstick, liner and cream eyeshadow from Laura Mercier.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2024/10/new-laura-mercier-caviar-collection-launch.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Smooth-Matte-Lipstick-swatches-deep.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3Y6YKQ4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eCaviar Lipsticks\u003c/a\u003e are a miss for me, however if you like a matte finish and find it challenging to find shades that are cool-toned enough, check these out. I know a number of you have told me my personal favorites for neutral lips sometime look straight up orange on you if you have fair or cool-toned complexion. This range has a lot of cooler undertones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eCaviar Perfecting Lip Liner\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Caviar Perfecting Lip Liner\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch. A look at the latest reformulations for lipstick, liner and cream eyeshadow from Laura Mercier.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2024/10/new-laura-mercier-caviar-collection-launch.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-review.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLast we have a look at the \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3N6LV1A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eCaviar Perfecting Lip Liner\u003c/a\u003e ($29). You girls know I am pretty brutal with lip liner reviews but I want to add a disclaimer that it’s mainly because my lips are on the pigmented side so most of those viral neutrals that look stunning on 99% of you just simply do not show up on me.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI think the new formula is a very nice classic kind of lip pencil. No fuss, nothing fancy, great tones, good pigment. They do feel a little dry on the lips but I really like how they adhere to the lips and they have a relatively smooth looking finish. Lasting power is very good. They aren’t the best but I do like the colors and if you’re looking to try something new I think they are worth checking out since they have a lot of great tones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" alt=\"Caviar Perfecting Lip Liner\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch. A look at the latest reformulations for lipstick, liner and cream eyeshadow from Laura Mercier.\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/2024/10/new-laura-mercier-caviar-collection-launch.html\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"New Laura Mercier Caviar Collection Launch\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1440x2160.jpg\" srcset=\"https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1440x2160.jpg 1440w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-67x100.jpg 67w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches-1080x1620.jpg 1080w, https://thebeautylookbook.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Laura-Mercier-Caviar-Perfecting-Lip-Liner-swatches.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOverall, I am very happy that the reformulated Caviar Stick Eyeshadows are a solid A+ formula still. I plan on taking a few of these with me on an upcoming trip. The mascara is also a solid A formula. I do like the tones and formula of the lip pencils, but I think there are better formulas out there like the new Glossier ones, Chanel, Pat McGrath, Huda Beauty to name a few. Lipsticks are a miss for me because of colors and scent, also I tend to not like matte finishes in general so I may have been a bit biased anyways.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou can find the Caviar Collection out now. Available at \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3TTMiR3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eNordstrom\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3TNhTUE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eSephora\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3TQUQIk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eKohl’s\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3TRzGtz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003eLaura Mercier\u003c/a\u003e and all other Laura Mercier retailers. Have you tried any of the new formulas? What did you think?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eCaviar Collection provided for review.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
